<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>112Hz 不平凡的共振 - 網路票根</title>
    <style>
        /* 基本背景設定 */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif;
        }

        /* 票根主體 */
        .ticket {
            width: 350px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* 圖片區域 */
        .ticket-header {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            background: url('bg.jpg') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        /* 內容區域 */
        .ticket-body {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* 資訊清單 */
        .info-list {
            text-align: left;
            border-top: 1px dashed #ccc;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .label { color: #999; }
        .value { color: #333; font-weight: 600; }

        /* 票根虛線切割效果 */
        .ticket::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: -10px;
            bottom: 120px;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .ticket::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            right: -10px;
            bottom: 120px;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* 底部裝飾 */
        .footer {
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="ticket">
        <div class="ticket-header"></div>
        
        <div class="ticket-body">
            <div class="title">112Hz</div>
            <div class="subtitle">不平凡的共振</div>
            
            <div class="info-list">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="label">演出時間</span>
                    <span class="value">2026 / 05 / 20 (待定)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="label">演出地點</span>
                    <span class="value">音樂廳 A 廳</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="label">座位資訊</span>
                    <span class="value">VIP 區 08 排 12 號</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="label">票券編號</span>
                    <span class="value">NO. 20260422-01</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            ADMIT ONE | 音樂會專屬票券
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
